about: Hi, I'm Satwika! I am an undergraduate student double majoring in Computer Science and Data Science at UC Berkeley. I am highly motivated to apply my technical knowledge for tangible real-world change. I am actively looking for internships in Software Engineering, Artificial Intelligence/Machine Learning, and Data Science roles to further develop my skill set. Feel free to reach out at paulsatwika6@berkeley.edu

projects_description: - Spearheaded the development of a cutting-edge PDF chatbot, facilitating users to effortlessly upload and query multiple PDFs and text documents- Leveraged a language model that generates responses by selecting the most semantically similar text chunks from the uploaded documents, utilizing text chunking, vector embeddings and similarity matching
